{"tid":792984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣開口同男朋友傾我地之間嘅問題？","createTime":"2018-08-25T04:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T16:45:49.000Z","uid":158220,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f6de950cf0fc29a9f94e455cc459d55f1c278d72","tid":792984,"uid":158220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"其實佢都對我好冷淡<br />\n諗返起以前再望下宜家<br />\n真係覺得好唏噓<br />\n<br />\n我whatsapp佢5句先覆一兩個字<br />\n仲成日已讀不回<br />\n有晚仲成晚唔知去左邊<br />\n宜家電話仲開始收收埋埋<br />\n唔知text邊個咁<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得咁樣冇可能唔係特登<br />\n佢應該都係想丟淡等我頂唔順講分手<br />\n<br />\n如果我攤開出黎講<br />\n應該都冇彎轉<br />\n我想知點先可以解決到個問題<br />\n有無人經歷過咁樣淡法可以挽救到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf97390317bbb444ff08a38c5038d729d09a1f94","tid":792984,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"屌咗未?"},{"pid":"93162352a61fdfd5b46c1e55d1c13297704963de","tid":792984,"uid":82414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"解決問題前提係雙方有心維繫"},{"pid":"5dcd8c35e872a1ccb7e8fd5e79a54828f0a8dd88","tid":792984,"uid":151664,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:17:16.000Z","msg":"whatsapp佢5句先覆一兩個字<br />\n仲成日已讀不回<br />\n<br />\n好明顯單方面同你分咗手，而你仲柒撚懵懵！<br />\n仲傾咩啫？？？<br />\n你真係好戇鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f7274d0ebe6e6f442af15d34e4ad40d7adea64","tid":792984,"uid":58374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"講咗一係改善<br />\n一係完<br />\n唔講就慢慢完 <br />\n又浪費時間<br />\n自己諗"},{"pid":"bf518db8df8dfe3d6f11d3713f75ca220adc64f0","tid":792984,"uid":51989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88d41acabc0795414a99076a511d3f231056d768","tid":792984,"uid":12